---
title: Goat Cheese & Caramelised Onion Pizza with Courgette & Rocket
description: Whip up a simple yet satisfying pizza with a combination of tasty ingredients. Caramelised onions plus tangy goat cheese bring the flavour, while courgette and rocket add essential greens. Enjoy this easy slice of life!
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/5beba6e9ae08b53b93056712-e6e89fe2.jpg
